{"an3.90:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 3.90 ","an3.90:0.2":"9. Samanavagga ","an3.90:0.3":"Dutiyasikkhattayasutta ","an3.90:1.1":"“Tisso ima, bhikkhave, sikkha. ","an3.90:1.2":"Katama tisso? ","an3.90:1.3":"Adhisilasikkha, adhicittasikkha, adhipannasikkha. ","an3.90:2.1":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, adhisilasikkha? ","an3.90:2.2":"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu silava hoti …pe… samadaya sikkhati sikkhapadesu. ","an3.90:2.3":"Ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, adhisilasikkha. ","an3.90:3.1":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, adhicittasikkha? ","an3.90:3.2":"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vivicceva kamehi …pe… catuttham jhanam upasampajja viharati. ","an3.90:3.3":"Ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, adhicittasikkha. ","an3.90:4.1":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, adhipannasikkha? ","an3.90:4.2":"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu asavanam khaya anasavam cetovimuttim pannavimuttim dittheva dhamme sayam abhinna sacchikatva upasampajja viharati. ","an3.90:4.3":"Ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, adhipannasikkha. ","an3.90:4.4":"Ima kho, bhikkhave, tisso sikkhati. ","an3.90:5.1":"Adhisilam adhicittam, ","an3.90:5.2":"adhipannanca viriyava; ","an3.90:5.3":"Thamava dhitima jhayi, ","an3.90:5.4":"sato guttindriyo care. ","an3.90:6.1":"Yatha pure tatha paccha, ","an3.90:6.2":"yatha paccha tatha pure; ","an3.90:6.3":"Yatha adho tatha uddham, ","an3.90:6.4":"yatha uddham tatha adho. ","an3.90:7.1":"Yatha diva tatha rattim, ","an3.90:7.2":"yatha rattim tatha diva; ","an3.90:7.3":"Abhibhuyya disa sabba, ","an3.90:7.4":"appamanasamadhina. ","an3.90:8.1":"Tamahu sekham patipadam, ","an3.90:8.2":"atho samsuddhacariyam; ","an3.90:8.3":"Tamahu loke sambuddham, ","an3.90:8.4":"dhiram patipadantagum. ","an3.90:9.1":"Vinnanassa nirodhena, ","an3.90:9.2":"tanhakkhayavimuttino; ","an3.90:9.3":"Pajjotasseva nibbanam, ","an3.90:9.4":"vimokkho hoti cetaso”ti. ","an3.90:9.5":"Dasamam. "}